{"type":null,"faqId":43839,"title":"WLAN不定时断开重连，提示\"已连接XXX网络\"怎么办？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:77.95pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:63.0pt list 77.95pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';tab-stops:list 77.95pt\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>1.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">连接</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">成功后，请保持在</span><span>\nWLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">热点的有效距离内，避免由于距离太远导致网络信号弱从而自动断开。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:106.3pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:77.95pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:63.0pt list 77.95pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';tab-stops:list 77.95pt\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>2.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">进入</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">设置界面，点击</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">高级设置</span><span> &gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">在休眠状态下保持</span><span>\nWLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">连接</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，选择</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">始终</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">。手机将始终保持与</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:\n'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">网络的连接。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:106.3pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><span><img width=\"496\" height=\"248\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150916205919105001.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:77.95pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:63.0pt list 77.95pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';tab-stops:list 77.95pt\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>3.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">若问题依然存在，请重新打开</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">开关或重启</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">热点。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:normal\"><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9340","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399556000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":8,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"i